Package: imf.data
Title: An Interface to IMF (International Monetary Fund) Data SDMX 3.0 API
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Pedro", "Baltazar",, "pedrobtz@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides low-level access to the International Monetary Fund
    SDMX 3.0 API and a concise workflow for discovering datasets,
    inspecting dimensions, and downloading observations as tidy data frames.
    API documentation is available from IMF Data Support
    (<https://datasupport.imf.org/knowledge?id=knowledge_category&category_id=9959b2bc1b6391903dba646fbd4bcb6a>).
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
